{"tid":1002965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【苦中作樂】誰是寒流襲美「元凶」? Elsa伊利諾州「被捕」","createTime":"2019-01-31T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T11:00:12.000Z","uid":75969,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d51609ca1f14c138218251cf67749230291e10","tid":1002965,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548865081_427d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548865081_427d.jpg&h=fcbc8d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">伊利諾州麥克萊恩巿警方在嚴冬中，苦中作樂，戲稱已「拘捕Elsa」。(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）極地漩渦（Polar Vortex）寒流吹襲美國，多個城巿的氣溫創新低，其中伊利諾州麥克萊恩巿（McLean）的警方決定苦中作樂，在社交媒體發放「拘捕」迪士尼動畫《魔雪奇緣》女主角Elsa的照片，寓意嚴寒天氣將過，為巿民打氣。<br />\n<br />\n麥克萊恩巿警方周二在Facebook貼上照片，顯示一名警員用粉紅色手扣，拘捕真人扮演的Elsa，並留言道：「由於極端嚴寒天氣的關係，所有罪案以及愚昧的行為，都必須中止。即使Elsa也要被拘捕，不准保釋，直到另行通知。」<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言表示，自己的女兒看到Elsa「被捕」後，哭了半個小時；有網民貼上自己女兒扮演Elsa的照片，說「警方拉錯人」。網民亦大改動畫歌曲的歌詞，要求「Let her go」（放她走）、又說「Do you wanna build a snowman in jail?」（想不想在獄中砌雪人？）<br />\n<br />\n不過，有眼利網民發現警方的照片並非原創，而是翻用南卡羅萊納州2015年遭寒流吹襲時的公關照片，希望麥克萊恩巿的警方尊重創意，說明清楚照片出處。<br />\n<br />\n伊利諾州周二已經進入緊急狀態，其中芝加哥的氣溫創1985年以來的新低，跌至華氏-21度（攝氏-29.4度），再加上陣風，令體感溫度低見華氏-51度（攝氏-46.1度）。<br />\n<br />\n霍士新聞  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190131/59205762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59205762&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6hA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=57566cbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59205762&h=3050e66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190131/59205762</a>"},{"pid":"e94f511b3f256bac569d321d914cc55e85f11e03","tid":1002965,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"女權仲唔上街抗議 警方打壓女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">快d凍撚死d女權撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e1ffe50007ad5b77bc407935a798a8d29991ea7","tid":1002965,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"扯左<br />\n<br />\n利申：有丁過冰雪奇緣"},{"pid":"dca04c9eed91208ef17f34a7b1d508ba7d9d1532","tid":1002965,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"又打氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068b50b4cb3d64c0fd5608e40fd5135477d65401","tid":1002965,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1ffe50007ad5b77bc407935a798a8d29991ea7","tid":1002965,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"扯左<br />\n<br />\n利申：有丁過冰雪奇緣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"拗返直個孿嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4455840195c128d563bf5b253e88c66a346452b","tid":1002965,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"拉鳩埋日谷番條柒頭啦"}]}